description:
Application focused on performing calculations and echocardiographic analysis, helping in the determination of diastolic dysfunction in common and special situations. The smart interface assists in the interpretation of the results.

Calculations and algorithms available in this version:
- Diastology (with analysis and calculation of variables);
- Fast diastology (optimized algorithm);
- Presence of myocardial disease;
- Volume of the LA (area-length, with one or two planes);
- LV Mass and Geometry;
- LVEF by Teichholz;
- Continuity equation;
- PISA (for both regurgitation and stenosis);
- Body surface area;
- Diastology in special populations (algorithms and calculators for hypertrophic cardiomyopathy, restrictive cardiomyopathy, mitral ring calcification, mitral stenosis, mitral regurgitation, sinus tachycardia, atrial fibrillation and more).
